com.guidewire.ab.external.entity

Interface GroupUserAssignmentState

  • All Superinterfaces:
    gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity, Versionable
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface GroupUserAssignmentState
extends Versionable, gw.pl.external.entity.Entity
    Joins a GroupAssignmentState entity to one or more Users. Also stores per user load information for round-robin assignment. This is an internal class which should only be used by the internals of the assignment engine.
